									d="M2 3H8C9.06087 3 10.0783 3.42143 10.8284 4.17157C11.5786 4.92172 12 5.93913 12 7V21C12 20.2044 11.6839 19.4413 11.1213 18.8787C10.5587 18.3161 9.79565 18 9 18H2V3Z"
